1. Install tomcat
2. Install mysql
3. Start mysql
4. Set the user name and password in to the application.properties
5. Upload the tomcat to eclipse
6. Eclipse only - Go to "web project settings" and change the "Context root" to: "/"
7. Upload the project to the eclipse tomcat
8. Run tomcat
9. Open the "web.html" in a browser
10 Start chatting!!!